name: Fishcoin
description: Fishcoin is a blockchain based traceability and data ecosystem designed specifically for the global seafood industry. It creates an incentive for data capture in various forms beginning with key data elements captured and communicated by fishermen and fish farmers at the point of harvest for the purpose of traceability. By addressing the critical incentive problem we are effectively creating an ecosystem for rewarding fishermen and supply chain intermediaries through micro- transactions, creating a virtuous cycle (carrot) for sustainable practices that extends beyond government mandates (stick) for traceability. The Fishcoin ecosystem is not a single application, but a series of decentralized open source tools designed to integrate with those used by the industry. By creating the appropriate reward structure for data capture along with an interoperable architecture, the Fishcoin ecosystem will allow for makers of third party tools such as IoT sensors and other data inputs to participate in the ecosystem and be rewarded accordingly. This will increase the velocity of data through supply chains and allow buyers to have a better understanding of the actual metrics that impact safety and quality.

GPU Audio’s novel approach allows for DSP (digital signal processing) to be offloaded onto the parallel processing architecture of GPUs at 1ms latency round-trip, allowing for truly next-gen features such as: limitless DSP plugin instances, remote computing and wireless/cloud processing, continuous audio rendering (no more exporting audio), and instantaneous results. Beginning with VST3 and AU functionality, we are redesigning the way DSP is handled so that developers and end-users alike can benefit immediately from the incredible power of GPUs to both enhance their existing products, and create the plugins and software of their dreams. Our mission is to provide a truly next-gen, qualitative level of performance for pro audio, and become the new standard of audio processing for the digital future across numerous verticals.

Our mission remains clear: to simplify and streamline the often complex processes of patent, trademark, design, and copyright registration for clients around the world. Here's what sets us apart: Global Reach: We have a presence in key regions across the globe, ensuring that our clients can protect their intellectual property rights wherever they do business. Efficiency: Time is of the essence when it comes to IP protection. We prioritize efficiency, helping you secure your intellectual property rights in a timely manner. Customized Solutions: No two clients are alike, and we tailor our services to meet your specific needs, whether you're a startup, a multinational corporation, or an individual inventor. While we prepare to launch our platform, we invite you to connect with us to explore how HumCen Global can empower your innovation ambitions through our services. Join us in the journey of safeguarding innovation on a global scale.
